# Security & Compliance Rules

- Encrypt all data at rest (AES-256) and in transit (TLS 1.3).
- Validate and sanitise all inputs server-side.
- Lock accounts after 5 failed login attempts.
- Scan uploaded files with ClamAV; restrict file types.
- Align with POPIA (South Africa) and GDPR (EU).
- Judges' digital signatures must meet legal standards for electronic evidence.
